commit.message:
Keep a README file

README is needed for autoreconf in bootstrap. From now, this file must exist.
Generate Makefile from Makefile.am via configure.ac

Remove autogenerated file

This file is generated by 'autoreconf' command, from 'bootstrap' script.

Use autoreconf

autoreconf command will create 'configure', 'Makefile.in' (from Makefile.am)
and other needed files. This is the modern mode to create a basic structure.
